{"nodes": [{"id": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_report", "label": "M3 Report \u2014 Model Building", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_arima", "label": "ARIMA (per-ticker, BIC order)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Order by BIC (parsimonious (1,0,0)/(0,0,1)) because AIC over-selected (2,0,2); causal append-then-forecast one-step after an off-by-one BLOCKER fix. Ties naive on holdout RMSE (DM p=0.78), directional coin flip (0.514)."}, {"id": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_gjr_garch", "label": "GJR-GARCH(1,1) Student-t", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Asymmetric o=1 (chosen because M2 proved the leverage effect), Student-t errors for fat tails (nu~5), evaluated as a variance model via QLIKE + Mincer-Zarnowitz not point RMSE. Its mean forecast is the one out-of-sample survivor (DirAcc 54.3%, binomial p=0.002) but is uneconomic after transaction costs. Originally mislabeled EGARCH; corrected by audit."}, {"id": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_attention_lstm", "label": "Global Attention LSTM", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Keras functional model, 60-day sequences + ticker one-hot, Bahdanau-style additive attention over timesteps, StandardScaler train-only, shuffle=False. Only a 2-epoch CPU smoke-test locally (RMSE 0.132 is plumbing, not a result); full training pending Colab GPU."}, {"id": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_lightgbm", "label": "LightGBM (tabular, exogenous)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "39 features + ticker categorical, deliberately un-tuned so the overfit is the lesson. 8/15 top importances are exogenous and it lifts val DirAcc to 0.539 (p=0.015), but holdout RMSE (0.02165) is significantly WORSE than naive (DM p=0.003) and direction is a coin flip (0.499)."}, {"id": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_exogenous_features", "label": "Exogenous Features (VIX/Yields/Dollar)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Nine leakage-safe macro features (vix_level, vix_log_change, vix_z_60, is_high_vol_regime, tnx_level, tnx_change, term_spread, term_spread_change, dxy_log_return) \u2014 the only break from price-history-only, all market-priced daily and known at close t (no CPI release-lag). Same-day VIX corr -0.70 vs next-day +0.05 proves no label contamination. MODEL_FEATURES 30->39."}, {"id": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_significance_testing", "label": "Directional Significance Testing (Binomial + Diebold-Mariano)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Added because a 55% DirAcc was read as skill without a test. Binomial test (DirAcc vs 0.50) + Diebold-Mariano (RMSE vs naive) on val and holdout exposed the val->holdout skill decay (GARCH val 0.555 p=0.0006 shrinks to 0.543 p=0.002)."}], "edges": [{"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_report", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_plans_milestone3_model_building_spec", "relation": "implements", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_report", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_arima", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_report", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_gjr_garch", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_report", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_attention_lstm", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_report", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_lightgbm", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_report", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_exogenous_features", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_report", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_significance_testing", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_report", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_project_decisions_and_architecture_emh", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_lightgbm", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_exogenous_features", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_lightgbm", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_project_decisions_and_architecture_emh", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_exogenous_features", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_data_processed_feature_dictionary_model_features", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "stock_market_trend_analysis_claude_multi_agent_audit", "target": "stock_market_trend_analysis_reports_milestones_m3_significance_testing", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "Stock-Market-Trend-Analysis/reports/milestones/M3.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}], "hyperedges": []}